---
description: "Code review standards for AID methodology"
globs: "**/*.{java,py,ts,js,cs,go,rs}"
alwaysApply: false
---
When reviewing code:
1. Check against task acceptance criteria
2. Verify alignment with .aid/knowledge/coding-standards.md
3. Ensure architectural consistency per .aid/knowledge/architecture.md
4. Grade A+ to F based on correctness, conventions, quality
5. Tag issues: CODE / TASK / SPEC / KB / ARCHITECTURE
